This is the first release of Automatic profile changer. Using this software you can set the time in which your will automatically get changed. For it only one thing you need to do is to first set the days of week and time and type of profile. We have given three type of profile for user which are Ringtone, Silent, Vibrate. In ringtone mode your mobile work as usual settings, in silent mode your mobile will become silent and in vibrate your will be in vibrate mode.
